title: >
  A reproducible downstream analysis framework for bulk RNA-seq
  using DESeq2 and functional enrichment

abstract: >
  This repository provides a reproducible, interpretation-focused
  downstream analysis pipeline for bulk RNA-seq experiments.
  The framework integrates DESeq2-based differential expression,
  comprehensive quality control, functional enrichment analysis
  (GO and KEGG over-representation analysis and GSEA),
  and publication-ready visualization and reporting.
  The pipeline is designed as a transparent and extensible analysis
  template for PhD students and researchers, emphasizing biological
  correctness, reproducibility, and interpretability rather than
  black-box execution.

